Long Description:

QuickOutline is a Chrome extension designed to help you easily navigate through a webpage's H1-H3 headers by providing a clean and organized outline in a popup. The purpose of this extension is to quickly display the page's outline, allowing you to save time and find the information you need faster.

Features:

Displays a convenient popup with clickable H1-H3 header links, allowing you to quickly navigate through the webpage.

Automatically scrolls to the corresponding section when clicking on a header link in the popup.

If a header has an empty string, it will not be displayed in the popup, keeping the outline clean and focused.

When there are no headers present on the webpage, the popup will show a "No header" message, informing the user of the absence of headers.

To use QuickOutline, simply click on the extension icon while browsing a webpage, and the popup will appear with the organized outline. Click on any header link to jump directly to that section. With QuickOutline, navigating webpages has never been easier or more efficient.

Try QuickOutline now and experience seamless webpage navigation!
